# PostgreSQL 18 Distribution

Target: @TARGET_TRIPLE@

This package contains PostgreSQL @POSTGRESQL_VERSION@ plus the extension set
installed into the same prefix.

Included dependency overlays:

- postgis_dependencies
- groonga
- fdw_dependencies
- v8

Installed extensions:

@INSTALLED_EXTENSIONS@

Skipped extensions:

@SKIPPED_EXTENSIONS@

Oracle Instant Client and IBM DB2 CLI are build-time/runtime inputs owned by
their vendors. When oracle_fdw or db2_fdw are built, this package includes only
the PostgreSQL extension files, not the vendor client libraries.

Linux packages also install systemd templates under `share/systemd/`:

- `postgresql18-dist.service`
- `postgresql18-dist.env`
